Overview 
Tonal is looking for an organized and detail-oriented professional to help support all aspects of our video production workflow and processes, support the implementation and execution of new systems and provide support to the Senior Production Manager in the functions of pre-production, studio/field production and post-production. 
You will be the primary support person to the Senior Production Manager on all aspects of production and studio operations. Responsible for carrying out the daily tasks in supporting our studio and field productions. 
You will work on a creative and growing LA-based video production team, focused on inventing and innovating brand-new forms of production. We focus on innovation, organization and extremely high quality, stretching what weâ€™re doing creatively while being extremely detail oriented along the way. 
What You Will Do 
Responsible for execution of all tasks and documentation needed to support the Senior Production Manager and Production Team in all aspects of physical production planning, prepping and execution.
 Manage all tasks and documents/details involved in ongoing studio production
 Coordinate all field shoots as needed Assist in creating and coordinating all talent and crew booking schedules Create call sheets, calendar invites and all support documents, as needed Request and acquisition of all certificates of insurance needed for vendors Handle additional requests as needed to support the daily operation of the studio and its shoots 
Who You Are 
Extremely organized, a passion for the details and keeping everything running smoothly Ability to work well under pressure and keep a cool head, fostering a positive creative environment Can work independently (self-starting) and within a team At least 2-4 years of physical production experience Experience in various production environments, from small to large Up to date on all the latest production workflow tools Experience communicating and coordinating with talent and crew Experience creating spreadsheets and documents Experience with or interest in learning Project Management tools 
